{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbf556abe-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11710"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"11710"},"text":"§ 11710.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Report","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The President shall, at the time the budget is submitted under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105"},"text":"section 1105 of title 31","children":[],"tail":", for each fiscal year transmit to the Congress a report on the progress made in meeting the objectives of this chapter, including a review of programs established or assisted pursuant to this chapter and an assessment and recommendations of additional programs or additional assistance necessary to, at a minimum, provide health services to Native Hawaiians, and ensure a health status for Native Hawaiians, which are at a parity with the health services available to, and the health status of, the general population."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbf556abf-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/579/s11"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–579, § 11","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-10-31"},"text":"Oct. 31, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/2923"},"text":"102 Stat. 2923","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/690/tII/s2311"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–690, title II, § 2311","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-18"},"text":"Nov. 18, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/4229"},"text":"102 Stat. 4229","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/396/tIX/s9168"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–396, title IX, § 9168","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-06"},"text":"Oct. 6, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/1948"},"text":"106 Stat. 1948","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbf556ac0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbf556ac1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idbf556ac2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The 1992 amendment is based on section 1 of S. 2681, One Hundred Second Congress, as passed by the Senate on ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-08-07"},"text":"Aug. 7, 1992","children":[],"tail":", and enacted into law by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/396/s9168"},"text":"section 9168 of Pub. L. 102–396","children":[],"tail":". Section 9168, which referred to S. 2681, as passed by the Senate on “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-09-12"},"text":"September 12, 1992","children":[],"tail":"”, has been treated as referring to S. 2681, as passed by the Senate on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-08-07"},"text":"Aug. 7, 1992","children":[],"tail":", to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s11709"},"text":"section 11709 of this title","children":[],"tail":" prior to the general amendment of this chapter by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/396"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–396","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"